title: Asian Female with Parasol

description: Oblong with curved sides, top and bottom, featuring raised decoration of woman in long, asian-style kimono, she holds parasol in left hand and reaches for planted, long-stemmed flower with right, background of suspended lanterns, plum blossoms and birds in flight.
